{"tid":2506583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「始作俑者」中國將向印度提供約1萬台製氧機","createTime":"2021-04-27T11:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T12:26:12.000Z","uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4129b175ad8bb0446772f4fab62f0695bb45ba8c","tid":2506583,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:46:51.000Z","msg":"中國將在一星期內，向印度提供大約1萬台製氧機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR3jFrKwJh7G12YhAGViJFxpzitFHJRmt7pZjk9JetgDZ?filename=ctUr4pS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctUr4pS.jpg&h=97cbdba4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於印度的武漢肺炎疫情持續惡化，中國駐斯里蘭卡大使館在社交網站表示，<span class=\"red\">昨日已由香港將800台製氧機空運至德里，一個星期內會有多1萬台，又表示中國正與印度保持溝通，討論印度的緊急需求。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587911-20210427.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587911-20210427.htm&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=cc0033ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587911-20210427.htm&h=d8b124a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587911-20210427.htm</a>"},{"pid":"80e6c35a67836f9c616241ef1377792664e29708","tid":2506583,"uid":37719,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:47:41.000Z","msg":"大人不記小人過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e09b44a9b646705e34ef13695d883b9747fe88a","tid":2506583,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"China Virus<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b7c7f2426f4f3ea3c9f03054d3d7b23a539e7c","tid":2506583,"uid":90392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedB